{"parse":{"title":"Runaan's Hurricane","pageid":746197,"wikitext":"{{Item info\n|goldvalue = \n|goldefficiency = \n|similaritems = Navori Flickerblade;Phantom Dancer;Rapid Firecannon;Fiendhunter Bolts;Kraken Slayer;Statikk Shiv;Yun Tal Wildarrows\n|background = \n|notes = \n[[File:Runaan's Hurricane hitbox.png|right|280px]]\n* {{sbc|Wind's Fury}} deals {{tip|basic damage}} and is tagged as {{tip|area damage|area of effect}} without applying {{tip|spell effects}}.\n* {{sbc|Wind's Fury}} is an [[auto-targeted]] effect.\n* {{sbc|Wind's Fury's}} bolts:\n** Deal the same damage type and apply the same hit effects as basic attacks would.\n*** This means that they {{tip|applies lifesteal|apply}} {{stil|life steal}}, trigger [[on-hit effects]] (excluding {{cai|W|Vayne}}), can {{tip|critically strike}}, draw {{tip|minion}} aggro and can be parried by effects such as {{tip|dodge}}, {{tip|block}}, and {{tip|blind}}.\n**** They will only critically strike if the primary attack would do so (with the exception of guaranteed critical strikes).\n**** They do not trigger [[on-attack effects]].\n** Are blockable {{tip|projectile|projectiles}}. \n** Have a missile speed of 2000.\n*** Of the unique override variants, {{cais|Q|Ashe}} and {{cai|Basic Attack|Kalista}} missiles are the only ones with a different speed of 2500.\n** Does not target [[structure]]s nor [[ward]]s.\n** Deals {{as|0 physical damage}} on-hit to the primary target that is able to stack {{iis|Black Cleaver}} {{nie|Carve}}.\n* {{sbc|Wind's Fury's}} damage is unaffected if the primary attack deals modified damage, with the exceptions of {{cai|Q|Ashe}} and {{cai|Switcheroo!|Jinx|Fishbones}}.\n* {{sbc|Wind's Fury}} will not trigger effects that were already consumed by the primary attack, but will do so if they are not consumed.\n* [[Shapeshifter|Shapeshifting]] champions can purchase '''Runaan's Hurricane''' but cannot trigger {{sbc|Wind's Fury}} without being in their {{tip|ranged}} form.\n* The movement speed stat stacks additively with other percentage movement speed modifiers.\n|strategy = \n* {{ii|Runaan's Hurricane}} is most effective when paired with on-hit effects that can be applied through its bolts.\n* {{ii|Runaan's Hurricane}} can also be used to increase the effectiveness of life steal since the bolts benefit from the stat with their damage.\n* {{ii|Runaan's Hurricane}} is highly effective in taking down multiple enemies at a time with its bolts.\n|oldicons = \n|trivia = \n* Runaan's Hurricane is named after [[Devon 'Runaan' Giehl]], an Associate Creative Designer at Riot Games.\n* {{ii|Runaan's Hurricane}} is actually a small floating orb that accompanies you around the battlefield, functioning similar to {{cai|Pix, Faerie Companion|Lulu}}.\n* The effect's name '''Wind's Fury''' is a reference to [https://warcraft.wiki.gg/wiki/Windfury_Weapon Windfury Weapon], a Shaman spell in '''World of Warcraft'''. \n* The item may have been inspired by the [[alpha items|alpha item]] {{ii|Hurricane|nolink=true}}, which was also a bow, though Hurricane's Alpha effect is unknown.\n* In {{w|Minecraft|Minecraft's}} [https://hypixelskyblock.minecraft.wiki/ Hypixel SkyBlock] server, there are two items named after '''Runaan's Hurricane''': the [https://hypixelskyblock.minecraft.wiki/w/Hurricane_Bow Hurricane Bow] and the [https://hypixelskyblock.minecraft.wiki/Runaan%27s_Bow Runaan's Bow].\n|quotes = \n|media = \n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" orientation=\"square\" spacing=\"small\">\nRunaan's Hurricane screenshot.png|Bolt VFX\n</gallery>\n|sfx = \n;Passive Triggered\n* {{sm2|Runaan's Hurricane passive SFX.ogg}} Attack Cast SFX\n* {{sm2|Runaan's Hurricane bolt fired SFX 2.ogg}} Attack Cast SFX\n* {{sm2|Runaan's Hurricane bolt fired SFX.ogg}} Attack Cast SFX\n* {{sm2|Runaan's Hurricane passive SFX 2.ogg}} Bolt SFX\n|revisions = \n|patchhistory = \n;[[V26.07]]\n* {{sbc|Bug Fix:}} Fixed a bug that caused the additional bolts to still deal damage and apply on hit effects while {{tip|blind|blinded}}.\n\n;[[V14.19]]\n* Total cost increased to {{g|2650}} from {{g|2600}}.\n** Combine cost increased to {{g|850}} from {{g|700}}.\n* Movement speed reduced to 4% from 7%.\n\n;[[V14.12]]\n* Combine cost increased to {{g|700}} from {{g|600}}.\n** Total cost unchanged.\n\n;[[V14.10]]\n* {{sbc|New Recipe:}} {{ii|Zeal}} + {{ii|Scout's Slingshot}} + {{g|600}} = {{g|2600}}.\n** {{sbc|Old Recipe:}} {{ii|Recurve Bow}} + {{ii|Zeal}} + {{g|1000}} = {{g|2800}}.\n* Critical strike chance increased to 25% from 20%.\n* {{sbc|Removed Unique Passive - Peck:}} Basic attacks deal {{as|30 '''bonus''' magic damage}} on-hit.\n* Wind's Fury bolt AD ratio increased to {{as|55% AD}} from {{as|40% AD}}.\n\n;[[V13.14]]\n* {{sbc|Undocumented:}} Peck damage increased to 30 from 15.\n* {{sbc|Undocumented:}} Wind's Fury AD ratio reduced to {{as|40% AD}} from {{as|50% AD}}.\n\n;[[V13.11]]\n* Peck damage reduced to 15 from 30.\n\n;[[V13.10]]\n* {{sbc|New Recipe:}} {{ii|Recurve Bow}} + {{ii|Zeal}} + {{g|1000}} = {{g|2800}}.\n** {{sbc|Old Recipe:}} {{ii|Dagger}} + {{ii|Zeal}} + {{ii|Dagger}} + {{g|950}} = {{g|2600}}.\n* Attack speed reduced to 40% from 45%.\n* {{sbc|New Unique Passive - Peck:}} Basic attacks deal {{as|30 '''bonus''' magic damage}} on-hit.\n* Wind's Fury AD ratio increased to {{as|50% AD}} from {{as|40% AD}}.\n* {{sbc|New Effect:}} Wind's Fury now additionally searches for any minions in range if no champions can be found.\n\n;[[V12.3]]\n* {{sbc|Bug Fix:}} Wind's Fury now correctly triggers from {{cai|Mystic Shot|Ezreal}} even when the missile travels a certain range.\n\n;[[V11.5]]\n* {{sbc|New Effect/Bug Fix:}} Attacks against secondary targets can now trigger {{iis|Titanic Hydra}} effect.\n* {{sbc|Bug Fix:}} Fixed a bug where the bolts would generate additional stacks of {{ri|Conqueror}}.\n\n;[[V11.2]]\n* Total cost increased to {{g|2600}} from {{g|2500}}.\n** Combine cost increased to {{g|950}} from {{g|850}}.\n* Attack speed increased to 45% from 40%.\n* {{sbc|Bug Fix:}